title: Oil rises as Syria fighting intensifies; U.S. hurricane worries fade
text:
Published By: Reuters - Business - Today 
SINGAPORE (Reuters) - Crude prices rose on Friday as fighting in Syria intensified, but remained on course to end the week largely unchanged...
